## Two variables 
$a_{1}x+b_{1}y=c_{1}$
$a_{2}x+b_{2}y=c_{2}$

$$D=\begin{vmatrix} 
    a_1 & b_1 \\
    a_2 & b_2 \\
\end{vmatrix}
$$
$$D_{x}=\begin{vmatrix} 
    c_1 & b_1 \\
    c_2 & b_2 \\
\end{vmatrix}
$$
$$D_{y}=\begin{vmatrix} 
    a_{1} & b_1 \\
    a_{2} & b_2 \\
\end{vmatrix}
$$
